metadata.name: 3VOLUTION vol.iii
metadata.description:
"not a dj", but young thrift gawd is a vibe whisperer est. lit nft gang discord days. They mixed music from my new album "EVOLUTION" into "3VOLUTION", a mini generative project perfect for the dance floor and the party in your headphones. Three celebratory volumes, three vibes, three destinations, and now vol. iii has landed on Decent! 

*all collectors welcome to join my inner circle, a token-gated hybrid community chatting about music, live-streams, cosmic tings, and irl meetups. visual art by a.i. charm music by charm taylor x young thrift gawd
